public void formatEmptyTarget()
Creates any nodes need to have enough to make the layout recognizable, removes any edges currently existing between the nodes, and then creates edges that correspond to this type of layout. This method is only valid if the layout was constructed as a manipulatable layout. This is because placeHolders have no meaning unless they are manipulatable.
